OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778429470
OL,3,CReform UK's ex-mayoral candidate set
OL,4,Cto become Walsall Council leader
OL,6,FThe remaining seats were split between
OL,7,Fthe Conservatives, who hold 10, the
OL,8,FWalsall Community Independents Party
OL,9,Fwith 8, and one councillor each for
OL,10,FLabour and the Independents.
OL,12,FWilliams said she is focused on local
OL,13,Fpriorities, including bringing
OL,14,Fbusinesses back into Walsall town
OL,15,Fcentre and helping struggling high
OL,16,Fstreets get back on their feet.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
