CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778429470
OL,3,CReform UK's ex-mayoral candidate set
OL,4,Cto become Walsall Council leader
OL,6,FDuring her mayoral campaign, she took
OL,7,Faim at what she called the "net zero
OL,8,Fagenda", arguing that climate change
OL,9,Fis not caused by human activity but is
OL,10,Fpart of a natural cycle of the planet.
OL,12,FShe also criticised so-called "anti-
OL,13,Fcar" policies, including low traffic
OL,14,Fneighbourhoods and clean air zones,
OL,15,Fsaying they were "seriously damaging
OL,16,Four businesses".
OL,18,FElaine Williams spoke to ITV News
OL,19,FCentral in 2024
OL,26,@oD@\OUpD@GO]tD@_OUuD@DO]wD@ROUxD@OO]
