PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1778429470
OL,3,CReform UK's ex-mayoral candidate set
OL,4,Cto become Walsall Council leader
OL,6,FAway from politics, Williams works as
OL,7,Fa solicitor, specialising in probate
OL,8,Flaw.
OL,10,FAt the same meeting on Saturday,
OL,11,FNicola Barker was elected deputy group
OL,12,Fleader and Peter Harrison was
OL,13,Fappointed secretary.
OL,15,FWilliams will still need to be
OL,16,Fformally confirmed as council leader
OL,17,Fwhen the full council meets on 18 May.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
