OL,3,CReform UK's ex-mayoral candidate set
OL,4,Cto become Walsall Council leader
OL,6,FElsewhere, in Birmingham, where Reform
OL,7,FUK is the largest group but without
OL,8,Foverall control - they're due to pick
OL,9,Fa group leader tomorrow.
OL,11,FElsewhere in Birmingham, Reform UK is
OL,12,Fthe largest group on the council but
OL,13,Fdoes not have overall control. The
OL,14,Fparty is due to pick its group leader
OL,15,Fon Monday.
OL,17,FIn Sandwell, Reform UK councillors are
OL,18,Fset to choose their group leader on
OL,19,FTuesday.
